@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@storeId = 1
@reviewId = 1

### List reviews by store (authenticated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/reviews/list
Authorization: {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}}
}

### Create review (CUSTOMER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/reviews
Authorization: {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}},
  "rating": 5,
  "content": "치킨이 정말 맛있었어요! 바삭하고 양도 많아서 만족합니다."
}

### Delete review (CUSTOMER or ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/reviews
Authorization: {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}},
  "reviewId": {{reviewId}}
}

###

# =============================================================================
# HMAC Verification — store-service :8082  (review endpoint)
# =============================================================================

### HMAC-1: Direct to backend — no headers → 401 Missing HMAC headers
POST http://localhost:8082/api/stores/reviews/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}}
}

###

### HMAC-2: Through BFF — signed automatically → 200
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stores/reviews/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}}
}

###

### HMAC-3: Direct to backend — valid timestamp, wrong signature → 401 Invalid HMAC signature
< {%
  request.variables.set("nowMs", Date.now().toString());
%}
POST http://localhost:8082/api/stores/reviews/list
Content-Type: application/json
X-Bff-Timestamp: {{nowMs}}
X-Bff-Signature: deadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeef

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}}
}

###

### HMAC-4: Direct to backend — expired timestamp → 401 Request expired
POST http://localhost:8082/api/stores/reviews/list
Content-Type: application/json
X-Bff-Timestamp: 1000000000000
X-Bff-Signature: anything

{
  "storeId": {{storeId}}
}
